<!-- ===== FAQ ===== -->
<div class="info-page">
  <div class="info-page__hero" style="background-image:url('https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0960/5588/6153/files/alexander-cream-2.jpg');">
    <div class="info-page__hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="container info-page__hero-inner">
      <p class="info-page__eyebrow">Got Questions?</p>
      <h1 class="info-page__hero-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
      <p class="info-page__hero-sub">Everything you need to know about Klawford beds, mattresses, delivery, and more.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container info-page__body">
    <div class="faq-nav">
      <button class="faq-nav__btn active" data-cat="delivery">Delivery</button>
      <button class="faq-nav__btn" data-cat="returns">Returns &amp; Trial</button>
      <button class="faq-nav__btn" data-cat="products">Products &amp; Quality</button>
      <button class="faq-nav__btn" data-cat="payment">Finance &amp; Payment</button>
      <button class="faq-nav__btn" data-cat="warranty">Warranty</button>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-group" data-cat="delivery">
        <h2 class="faq-group__title">Delivery</h2>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">How long does delivery take?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>All Klawford orders to UK mainland are delivered within <strong>7–14 working days</strong>. You'll receive an email when dispatched with a tracking link, plus SMS updates on the day of delivery.</p></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">Is delivery really free?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Yes — standard delivery to all UK mainland addresses is completely free on every Klawford order, with no minimum spend. Remote areas may incur a surcharge — contact us for a quote.</p></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">Do you offer weekend or evening deliveries?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Weekend and evening slots are available in select postcodes. Contact <strong>sales@clickclickstore.co.uk</strong> before ordering and we'll do our best to accommodate you.</p></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">What happens if I'm not home?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Our courier will leave a card to rearrange. We recommend providing a phone number so we can give you advance notice. You can also contact us directly to reschedule.</p></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">Do you deliver to Northern Ireland or Ireland?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Yes — delivery to Northern Ireland and the Republic of Ireland is available. Charges vary, so please contact us at <strong>sales@clickclickstore.co.uk</strong> for a personalised quote.</p></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">What is White Glove delivery?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Our White Glove service means a specialist two-person team delivers to your chosen room, assembles your bed frame, and removes all packaging. Old bed/mattress removal is available for an additional charge.</p></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-group" data-cat="returns" style="display:none;">
        <h2 class="faq-group__title">Returns &amp; Trial</h2>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">What is your returns policy?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>All Klawford mattresses come with a <strong>60-night sleep trial</strong>. If not completely satisfied, contact us and we'll arrange a free collection and full refund. Beds and frames can be returned within 14 days if unused and in original packaging.</p></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">How do I start a return?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Email <strong>sales@clickclickstore.co.uk</strong> with your order number and reason for return. We'll confirm eligibility and arrange free collection at a time that suits you.</p></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">Why do I need to sleep on the mattress for 14 nights first?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Your body naturally takes time to adjust to a new sleep surface. We ask for 14 nights minimum to give you the full benefit. After that, if you're still not happy, we're here to help.</p></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">How long does a refund take?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Once your mattress is collected, refunds are processed within <strong>5–7 working days</strong> to your original payment method.</p></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">Do I need the original packaging to return?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>No — original packaging is not required for mattress returns under the 60-night trial. For bed frames, original packaging is required.</p></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">Do I need a mattress protector?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Yes — a mattress protector must be used throughout the trial for hygiene purposes. This is a condition of our 60-night trial.</p></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-group" data-cat="products" style="display:none;">
        <h2 class="faq-group__title">Products &amp; Quality</h2>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">What bed sizes do you offer?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Klawford beds are available in all standard UK sizes: <strong>Small Single (2'6), Single (3'), Small Double (4'), Double (4'6), King (5'), and Super King (6')</strong>. Availability varies by product.</p></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">Are Klawford beds handmade?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Yes. Every Klawford bed is <strong>handcrafted in the UK</strong> by skilled artisans using premium materials. Each piece is built to order and made to last.</p></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">What types of beds do you sell?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Our collection includes divan beds, ottoman storage beds, panel beds, wing-back beds, and luxury upholstered frames, plus pocket sprung and memory foam mattresses.</p></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">Can I choose my own fabric or colour?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Many beds are available in multiple fabrics and colours, selectable on the product page. For bespoke requests, please contact our team.</p></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">How do I care for my mattress?</button><div class="faq-a"><p><strong>Rotate it 180° every 3 months</strong>, always use a protector, keep it ventilated, and spot clean with mild detergent. Do not fold or bend your mattress.</p></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">What firmness mattresses do you offer?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Available in <strong>Soft, Medium, Medium Firm, Firm, and Extra Firm</strong>. Side sleepers typically prefer softer; back sleepers medium to firm; stomach sleepers firm to extra firm.</p></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-group" data-cat="payment" style="display:none;">
        <h2 class="faq-group__title">Finance &amp; Payment</h2>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">Do you offer finance or pay monthly?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Yes — Klawford offers flexible finance options through trusted payment partners. Apply at checkout. Representative APR and eligibility displayed at the point of application.</p></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">What payment methods do you accept?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>We accept all major credit/debit cards (Visa, Mastercard, Amex), PayPal, Apple Pay, Google Pay, and finance options. All payments are processed securely via SSL encryption.</p></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">Can I change or cancel my order?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Orders can be amended or cancelled within <strong>24 hours</strong> of placing. Because our beds are made to order, we're unable to cancel after production begins. Email us immediately at <strong>sales@clickclickstore.co.uk</strong>.</p></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-group" data-cat="warranty" style="display:none;">
        <h2 class="faq-group__title">Warranty</h2>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">What warranty do Klawford products come with?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>All Klawford beds and mattresses come with a <strong>manufacturer's guarantee</strong> covering structural faults and manufacturing defects. Warranty periods are listed on each product page.</p></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">What does the warranty cover?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Manufacturing defects including structural failures, faulty joints, and material defects under normal domestic use. Does not cover wear and tear, misuse, or improper assembly.</p></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">How do I make a warranty claim?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Email <strong>sales@clickclickstore.co.uk</strong> with your order number, a description of the issue, and clear photographs. We'll respond within 2 working days.</p></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">My item arrived damaged — what should I do?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Note it on the delivery paperwork, photograph the damage, and contact us within <strong>48 hours</strong> of delivery. We'll arrange a replacement or repair at no cost to you.</p></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="info-cta">
      <h2 class="info-cta__title">Still Have a Question?</h2>
      <p class="info-cta__text">Our team is available Monday–Friday and would love to help you find the perfect bed or mattress.</p>
      <a href="mailto:sales@clickclickstore.co.uk" class="btn btn--primary">Email Our Team</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
(function(){
  document.querySelectorAll('.faq-q').forEach(function(btn){
    btn.addEventListener('click',function(){
      var item=this.closest('.faq-item'),open=item.classList.contains('is-open');
      item.closest('.faq-group').querySelectorAll('.faq-item').forEach(function(i){i.classList.remove('is-open');i.querySelector('.faq-q').setAttribute('aria-expanded','false');});
      if(!open){item.classList.add('is-open');this.setAttribute('aria-expanded','true');}
    });
  });
  document.querySelectorAll('.faq-nav__btn').forEach(function(btn){
    btn.addEventListener('click',function(){
      var cat=this.getAttribute('data-cat');
      document.querySelectorAll('.faq-nav__btn').forEach(function(b){b.classList.remove('active');});
      this.classList.add('active');
      document.querySelectorAll('.faq-group').forEach(function(g){g.style.display=g.getAttribute('data-cat')===cat?'':'none';});
    });
  });
})();
</script>

{%- else -%}

